mementoheaders-desc: The Memento Headers extension provides the just the HTTP headers for Memento clients, allowing Memento users to browse old versions of web pages as if it were the past date that the user choses.  Please visit http://mementoweb.org for more information.
bad-title: The title object for this page did not load correctly, please check your MediaWiki installation.
bad-current-revision: The revision given for this page did not load correctly.
bad-first-rev: Could not retrieve the first revision object for this page
bad-last-rev: Could not retrieve the last revision object for this page
bad-first-id: Could not retrieve the first revision id for this page
